<h2>About the 2024 Adventure Series</h2>
<section class="opener">
    <p>Welcome to the 2024 Redwood Adventure Cycling (RAC) Adventure Series. What is the Adventure Series you ask? It is
        a curated, self-guided cycling series for those seeking adventure along the trails and roads less traveled in
        and around Humboldt County, California. The Adventure Series allows you to ride amazing routes at your leisure,
        take beautiful photos, collect points, and win prizes! And the best part - it's completely free.</p>
</section>

